description:
Pianist Christian Sands talks about his relationship with the late Dr. Billy Taylor, a longtime mentor. Sands also recalls meeting and playing with Taylor, along with other jazz masters Barry Harris and Oscar Peterson.   

This video interview was done for JazzTimes during the 2015 Cruise, on which Sands was performing with Christian McBride and Ulysses Owens, Jr. Interview by Irene Lee.  Video by Lee Mergner.

For more information about Sands, go to www.christiansandsjazz.com

For more information about The Jazz Cruise, go to www.thejazzcruise.com

For more information about JazzTimes, go to www.jazztimes.com
